199
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:44,420
BU GURU CHIHUAHUA
KAU LEBIH CANTIK SAAT TIDUR

200
00:13:44,490 --> 00:13:45,460
Apa?

201
00:13:46,460 --> 00:13:49,730
Seperti ini, lalu garis lagi, lalu lurus…

202
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:53,900
Bu Guru…

203
00:13:56,070 --> 00:13:58,440
Di kiri.

204
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,210
Itu salah!

205
00:14:03,280 --> 00:14:04,320
Maaf.

206
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:09,450
Itu tak muat.

207
00:14:19,690 --> 00:14:20,790
Sempurna.

208
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:25,640
BU GURU CHIHUAHUA KAU TERLIHAT

209
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:26,530
Kau…

210
00:14:27,970 --> 00:14:28,800
Cantik…

211
00:14:28,870 --> 00:14:30,640
LEBIH CANTIK

212
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:31,530
Lebih cantik.

213
00:14:34,270 --> 00:14:35,740
Apa itu benar?

214
00:14:36,710 --> 00:14:38,950
Begitu, lalu…

215
00:14:40,780 --> 00:14:42,680
Dia mempelajari beberapa kanji baru.

216
00:14:44,050 --> 00:14:47,050
Menulis surat ini
pasti lebih sulit untuk dia

217
00:14:47,620 --> 00:14:49,960
daripada membuatkan aku sarapan.

218
00:14:54,890 --> 00:14:55,760
Selesai!

219
